name: Get Fit Plan
meal1:
1/2 cup egg whites scrambled with 1 teaspoon olive oil, 1 teaspoon chopped basil, 1 teaspoon grated Parmesan, and 1/2 cup cherry tomatoes
1 slice whole-grain toast
1/2 cup blueberries
1 cup skim milk
meal2: 1/2 cup fat-free Greek yogurt topped with 1/4 cup sliced strawberries
meal3: Salad made with: 3/4 cup cooked bulgur, 4 ounces chopped grilled chicken breast, 1 tablespoon shredded low-fat cheddar, diced grilled veggies and 1 tablespoon low-fat vinaigrette
meal5: 4 ounces grilled salmon 1 cup wild rice with 1 tablespoon slivered toasted almonds 1 cup wilted baby spinach with 1 teaspoon each olive oil, balsamic vinegar
